22	 *
23	 * Query params:
24	 * @param locationId {string} Required. The location to fetch hourly revenue for.
25	 * @param timePeriod {string} Optional. Time window descriptor. Defaults to '24h'.
26	 * @param startDate  {string} Optional. ISO datetime string for the start of a custom range.
27	 * @param endDate    {string} Optional. ISO datetime string for the end of a custom range.
28	 */
